dc_title_s: Caribbean Sea, Honduras, Isla de Utila (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hahcures and spot heights. "From a British survey in 1835." "Copyright 1996 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes tidal information. Inset: Bancos Salmedina. Scale 1:37,420. Map NO.28143 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA). United States. Defense Mapping Agency. (1996). Caribbean Sea, Honduras, Isla de Utila (Raster Image). LandInfo. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/st047mf4777 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
